{"tid":1365080,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"光復元朗記得一定要戴口罩！！","createTime":"2019-07-25T13:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T14:22:00.000Z","uid":231469,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"38a853b4a9a0c8a250cdc0f0145708163451750a","tid":1365080,"uid":231469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:53:59.000Z","msg":"發夢好多次遊行 好多人都唔戴口罩 我知道係好熱 好焗 但係今次真係一定要戴！有兩個原因。<br />\n<br />\n1）打破白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n啲黑社會就話著黑衫 戴口罩就打 咁我地就更加要著黑衫戴口罩，夠膽就黎打我地！我地唔會怕你！！<br />\n<br />\n2）以防被點相<br />\n<br />\n始終對家係黑社會，比佢地點左相有可能無啦啦夜晚晚搵人打你，所以大家一定要好好保護自己，一定唔可以比人認到！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁多位加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4338c4a58a4e29ff2adf972de9b95f4e4c4766d6","tid":1365080,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:54:44.000Z","msg":"仲諗緊出唔出元朗好<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1364858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1364858</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5d4cb6562e814899f63e496294e9f8c985d76dc7","tid":1365080,"uid":231469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:56:26.000Z","msg":"推！！！ 要識得保護自己！"},{"pid":"c8451066713c53c988b47dadb28a3e55827fed99","tid":1365080,"uid":193328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:05:33.000Z","msg":"其實，你地唔好行大馬路，行每年舞龍舞獅嘅路線咪安全囉？咪唔會有唔安全嘅理由"},{"pid":"a1dc2b5f927c7fa15b1bc13975beeadd79ab2720","tid":1365080,"uid":127858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:16:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">兄弟爬山</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">各有各做</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" cla